#. Add-on description
#. Translators: Long description to be shown for this add-on on add-on information from add-on store
#: buildVars.py:13
msgid ""
"An advanced AI assistant for NVDA using Gemini models.\n"
"Command Layer: Press NVDA+Shift+V, then:\n"
"- Smart Translator (T) / Clipboard (Shift+T)\n"
"- Text Refiner (R)\n"
"- Describe Object (V) / Full Screen (O)\n"
"- Online Video Analysis (Shift+V)\n"
"- Document Reader (D)\n"
"- File OCR (F)\n"
"- CAPTCHA Solver (C)\n"
"- Audio Transcription (A)\n"
"- Smart Dictation (S)\n"
"- Announce Status (I)\n"
"- Label Object (L)\n"
"- Manage/Scan Labels (Shift+L)\n"
"- UI Explorer (E)\n"
"- AI Operator (Shift+A)\n"
"- Check Update (U)\n"
"- Recall Last Result (Space)\n"
"- Commands Help (H)"
msgstr ""
"Gemini modellerini kullanan NVDA için gelişmiş bir yapay zeka asistanı.\n"
"Komut Katmanı: NVDA+Shift+V tuşlarına basın, ardından:\n"
"- Akıllı Çevirmen (T) / Pano (Shift+T)\n"
"- Metin İyileştirici (R)\n"
"- Nesne Tanımlama (V) / Tam Ekran (O)\n"
"- Çevrimiçi Video Analizi (Shift+V)\n"
"- Belge Okuyucu (D)\n"
